quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,Ndarahiye kuri iki camwa citiriweTtiyn na Zaytuni
  95,2,No k’umusozi wa Sinayi
  95,3,No kuri iki gisagara c’amahoro c’IMakkat
  95,4,Ntankeka twaremye umuntu mw’ishusho ryiza cane
  95,5,Hanyuma tumugarura kuba hasi gusumba abari hasi cane
  95,6,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza,\tabo nibo bazoronka impembo itazo hera"
  95,7,N’igiki kigushikira n’uguhakana impembo munyuma y’ukubona ivyo vyose
  95,8,Ntabwo Allah arenganura abacamanza